subject: Lacrosse
College Athletics
NCAA Lacrosse Championships
lead_paragraph: Unseeded Maryland beat top-seeded Syracuse, 6-5, in Foxborough, Mass., to advance to the N.C.A.A. men’s tournament semifinals.
